data.description: ***PRICE REDUCTION***SOUGHT AFTER VIBRANT COMMUNITY***Location Location Location!  This Condo located in the upscale and meticulously maintained residential 55+ community. Your building is luxuriously modern and has beautiful architecture. Outside your curb appeal bursts with lush landscaping. Your condo unit is on the 4th floor,  giving you a patio with a view. You have your own garage (#20) just a short walk to your building entrance and includes additional storage space. When you enter your home, you are welcomed by a spacious and open floorplan. Your design is contemporary and the cool tones of the interior create your own sanctuary. Your windows allow plenty of natural light to fill the living space.  The ample kitchen is any cook's dream.  You have all of the appliances and counter space needed to prepare a glorious holiday meal for the family or an intimate mid week meal. There's room for a breakfast table.  An ample pantry provides plenty of storage space for all your kitchen essentials. Your kitchen flows directly into the dining area, making it perfect for entertaining guests. Your condo boasts two well-appointed bedrooms. Your Owners Suite is spacious and features a walk-in closet. The en-suite bathroom is a wonderful spa retreat, complete with a soaking tub, a separate shower, and dual vanities. The second bedroom is equally comfortable and has its bathroom just steps from the door.   Community Amenities: The 55+ community offers an impressive array of amenities, including: A clubhouse where residents can gather for social events and activities. An indoor and outdoor pool for year-round swimming. A well-equipped workout facility to help residents stay active and healthy. Pool tables and other recreational spaces for leisurely enjoyment. Landscaped walking paths and green spaces for outdoor relaxation. Living in this condo within the 55+ community means having access to a vibrant and engaging lifestyle with a strong sense of community. It's a place where you can enjoy your golden years in style and comfort, surrounded by like-minded individuals and a wealth of amenities to enhance your daily life.
